-- ALTER VIEW univmed.dim_consent_history
-- AS
SELECT
 [KEY_CRM_EMAIL]
,[CRM_PAINEL]
,[DATA_VEEVA]
,[EMAIL_VEEVA]
,[CONSENT_VEEVA_1_1]
,[CONSENT_VEEVA_1_MASS]
,[ROW_ID_CONTATO_VEEVA]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Universo Medico/dimensao_consent_history.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
 [KEY_CRM_EMAIL]         VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CRM_PAINEL]			 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DATA_VEEVA]			 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_VEEVA]			 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CONSENT_VEEVA_1_1]	 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CONSENT_VEEVA_1_MASS]	 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_CONTATO_VEEVA]	 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
